    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（――“得体の知れないもの”の答えは）\n（見つからないまま、朝がやって来た）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Morning arrives‚ and I still haven’t found an answer）\n（for the source of this “unknown element.”）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "にゃーーーーーー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Meowwww!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.166666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.633333333333331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "またネコか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Found another cat?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.833333381017049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "違うよ。今日はもっと凄いもの\n……あ、{user}さんも見る？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nope‚ something even more amazing.\nOh‚ {user}-san‚ you wanna see?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.732562398910517,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　いや、いいよ。急いでるし\nそれより一人で下りられるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? No‚ it’s fine. I’m in a hurry.\nWill you be able to get down on your own this time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.332562398910515,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "えーーー\nちょっとだけだから、見ていってよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehhhh?\nC’mon‚ just for a sec. Watch with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.340748135248816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "ね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.57408146858215,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとだけだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just for a sec.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.640748135248817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（かなり高いな……）\n（実際、芽衣はどうやって登ったんだろう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She’s up really high.）\n（I wonder how Mei even managed to climb up.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.97408144474029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "あれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.638571254412334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（――指さしたのは近くの家の窓だ）\n（髪を振り乱す女の子の顔がチラリと横切る）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She points to the window of a house nearby.）\n（I catch a glimpse of a girl waving her hair back and forth.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.83857125441233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（――彼女は踊っていた。ステップも綺麗で）\n（動きのキレから、かなりの練習量が窺える）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She’s dancing. Her steps are graceful.）\n（Her moves are clean. It’s obvious she’s practiced a lot.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.87190458774567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……誰なんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who is she?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.89757368564606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "さあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No idea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.43090701897939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "知らないで見てたのっ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ve been spying on her without permission?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.30827666123708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "なんかね、凄いなあっていつも思ってて\nあたしも、練習したらあんな風に踊れるのかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just find her amazing.\nI wonder if I could dance like that if I practiced as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.57494332790373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（――よっ、というかけ声と共に）\n（芽衣は塀の上に立った）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mei lets out an “Umph!”）\n（and stands on top of the wall.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.14160999457037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "危ないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Careful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.9749433279037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "平気平気\nこういう所は慣れてるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m fine.\nI’m used to this kinda thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.07494332790372,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ダンス、好きなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you like dancing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.37882093191145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "うん\nなんか、自分がキラキラしたものになった気がするから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah.\nIt makes me feel all sparkly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.53249445358908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "（――その笑顔を見た瞬間）\n（俺の頭の中に、何かが閃いた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The instant I see her smile）\n（something flashes through my mind.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.73249445358907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "ん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4658277869224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "……そうか……そうだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right… That’s it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.63249445358906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "何？\n何何何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?\nWhat‚ what‚ what?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.56281188726422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣\nいや、早坂芽衣さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei\nNo‚ Mei Hayasaka.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.7259954855556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？\nあ……な、何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?\nUh… Wh-what?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.17223141250152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "あなたに話が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have something to ask you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.49556477921344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "きゃーーーーーーー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eeeek!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.31223146972197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob1",
      "speakerName": "？？？",
      "speakerNameEn": "？？？",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今、覗いてたわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were spying on me‚ weren’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 108.50093894061584
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いや……これは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ no… You see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.47955577430268,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_05-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "うん\n覗いてたよーー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah.\nWe were!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.54517937558037,
      "sfxList": []
